wherigo_decompile_message:
Unfortunately, the GC Wizard cannot extract the Details - LUA code - offline at the moment. If you like, the cartridge (and nothing else!) will be send to our server for analysis.

Alternatively you can put manually decompiled LUA code directly into the tool from a file or an internet resource.
To get the decompiled LUA code you can use for example the WIG-crumbler from Team Hildesheim at https://wigcrumbler.team-hildesheim.de/en_US/.

Meanwhile we are searching for an offline solution.
